{%- comment -%}
  Dedicated page template for the Skier DNA experience.
  Place at: templates/page.skier-dna.json  (Online Store 2.0 JSON template)

  Create a Shopify page (e.g. /pages/skier-dna) and assign it this template.
  The theme's GLOBAL HEADER and FOOTER (sections/header + footer in the theme's
  layout/theme.liquid) render automatically above and below this — you do NOT
  add them here and must NOT rebuild them inside the experience. This template
  only owns the page BODY, which is the single Skier DNA section.

  Because Skier DNA is just a section, it could technically be added to other
  2.0 templates too — but for Phase 1 this dedicated page is the ONE entry
  point. Don't build for product-page/modal embedding; it's out of scope.
{%- endcomment -%}
{
  "sections": {
    "skier_dna": {
      "type": "skier-dna",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "Let's find your ski.",
        "subhead": "Answer a few questions and watch the ski we'd build for you come to life."
      }
    }
  },
  "order": ["skier_dna"]
}
